OL,5, Kate Garraway has said the cost of care
OL,6, for her late husband Derek Draper has  
OL,7, left her with huge debts.              
OL,9,FShe was speaking in her latest         
OL,10,Fdocumentary, Kate Garraway: Derek's    
OL,11,FStory. Draper died aged 56 from the    
OL,12,Flong-term effects of Covid, in January.
OL,14,FWhile acknowledging her job as a       
OL,15,Fpresenter on GMB was well-paid,        
OL,16,FGarraway said the #16,000-a-month care 
OL,17,Fcosts were more than her ITV salary.   
OL,19,FDraper is heard speaking on camera     
OL,20,Fduring the programme.                  
